 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanessa_Gilles\", \"score\": 0.9999984015950345, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vanessa Gilles\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanessa_Gilles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanessa_Gilles\"}, {\"begin\": 155, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9854649980555784, \"rank\": 0.013878018187798971, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assistant coach Jasmine Mander and analyst Joey Lombardi were sent home from the Games in Paris on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"score\": 0.9995697869954018, \"rank\": 0.0003730424351029807, \"text\": \"Jasmine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasmine\"}, {\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joey_Tribbiani\", \"score\": 0.9999934614684239, \"rank\": 5.956437121785001e-06, \"text\": \"Joey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joey_Tribbiani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joey_Tribbiani\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992869562, \"rank\": 7.131366982932883e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lombardi was also given a suspended eight-month prison sentence for flying a drone over a New Zealand training session in Saint-Etienne in the build-up to the match.\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9854649980555784, \"rank\": 0.013878018187798971, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz_Cathedral\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.066748189732812e-13, \"text\": \"Saint-Etienne\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q1370598\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz_Cathedral\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz_Cathedral\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FIFA has since opened disciplinary proceedings against\\u00a0Canada.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999971811324653, \"rank\": 2.2970429910689082e-06, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999547526, \"rank\": 4.0814729158784145e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, it wasn't easy,\\\" Gilles told reporters.\", \"from\": 567, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of emotion, frustration and humiliation because as a player, it does not reflect our values and what we want to represent as competitors at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Games represent fair play.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Canadians, these are not our values or those of our country.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not cheats.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very hard but we knew how to be united.\\\"\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada\\u00a0are defending their Olympic title in Paris after defeating Sweden to win gold in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999547526, \"rank\": 4.0814729158784145e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992869562, \"rank\": 7.131366982932883e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999367496379368, \"rank\": 6.32378491765874e-05, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9985802836138234, \"rank\": 0.0014171956937463603, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's up to us to stay together and try not to let social media and the press break into our bubble,\\\" added on-loan Lyon defender Gilles.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been able to do that in the past.\\\"\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Head coach Bev Priestman also took no part in the game after the controversy, but is expected to be back on the bench for\\u00a0Canada's second Group A match against France on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bev_Priestman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bev Priestman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bev_Priestman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bev_Priestman\"}, {\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999547526, \"rank\": 4.0814729158784145e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999995866807823, \"rank\": 4.120618332295897e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She took a step back from this match and left the bench to her assistants but for the next matches, she should take her place again,\\\" said Gilles.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goals from Arsenal forward Cloe Lacasse and Evelyne Viens helped\\u00a0Canada\\u00a0come from behind to win.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9velyne_Viens\", \"score\": 0.9999997565203399, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evelyne Viens\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9velyne_Viens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9velyne_Viens\"}, {\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999547526, \"rank\": 4.0814729158784145e-11, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand coach Michael Mayne refused to blame the spying incident on his side's loss.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9854649980555784, \"rank\": 0.013878018187798971, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Mayne\", \"score\": 0.9999651629472831, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Mayne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q42603\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Mayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Mayne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to make excuses for this result,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, yes, we are disappointed.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is the question of how this happened and the reasons that led to this situation.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, maybe it influenced part of the game.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to play and we did our best.\\\"\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand next face Colombia on Sunday, needing to avoid defeat to give their quarter-final hopes a boost.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9854649980555784, \"rank\": 0.013878018187798971, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8591619771681482, \"rank\": 0.1639248741416688, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": []}]}"